The paper addresses the problem of developing on-line visual tracking algorithms, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The specialized communication protocol presented in the paper can be used for algorithm evaluation, which is also related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions a reference implementation of the protocol that makes it easy to use in several popular programming languages, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
